                      <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> So yeah I havent done this before beleive it or not.  <br /><br />But yesterday I was in ME cause my acryila camp sucks now listenign to ppl talking about charm fighting.<br /><br />So I listend in and I was at the same fighting spot so I desided to try it.<br /><br />So yeah it was insane xp once I got the technique down.  Nothing like keeping the bat field clear the 2 coterie houses empty and the drudge feild empty.  I was averaging an aa every hour or so.  <br /><br />So here was my technique.  I found a reanimated drudge charmed with thrall.<br /><br />Hasted he was now a death machine.<br /><br />pulled with slow sicked him.  Rooted mob I was fighting so if charm broke I wouldnt have 2 mobs on me.<br /><br />Sat back at maximum distance with a twitchy finger on st and my pet targeted if charm broke.  I did this for 8 hours.  Got 6 aa and maxed 60 no deaths.  Insane xp.<br /><br />man magelo.<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=407287" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=407287</a></span id="msg"></font>
